1.2.0
 	 - Added support for OpenOTP v1.2 and FIDO U2F authentication. 
1.1.0 
	 - Plugin has been completely re-writen.
	 - Changed the plugin behavior with OpenOTP Challenge-Response.
	   > The plugin displays an overlay on Challenge-Response session.
	   > No modification of the RoundCube login form.

1.0.2
     - Added support for OpenOTP v1.1 and SimpleLogin method.
       The plugin will now transparently support any OpenOTP Login Mode including:
       > LDAP only
       > OTP only
       > LDAP+OTP with user challenge-response

1.0.1
     - Added compatibility with OpenOTP 1.0.17.
     - Added support for location-based policies in WebADM 1.2.3 & OpenOTP 1.0.17.

1.0.0
     Initial public release.
